  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ミッキーマウスは思い出の道を歩き、彼が経験した時を超えた冒険を振り返るチャンスを得ます。『ミッキーマニア』は、すべてのレベルがミッキーの最も有名なアニメーションに基づいたプラットフォーマーです。レベルは約75年にわたり、「蒸気船ウィリー」から「王子と乞食」まで続きます。\n\nゲームプレイは主に敵に対してジャンプし、ビー玉を投げることが中心で、時折パズル要素も含まれています。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Mickey Mouse gets a chance to go down memory lane and walk through the timeless adventures he has lived. Mickey Mania is a platformer where all the levels are based on Mickey's most famous cartoons. The levels range about 75 years, starting off with \"Steamboat Willie\" and going all the way to \"The Prince and the Pauper\".\n\nThe gameplay consists mostly of jumping and marble throwing at enemies, with an occasional puzzle element.\n\nThe Sega Genesis version has an additional level not present in the Super NES version, released a month prior.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "1994 video game developed by Traveller's Tales",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
